,{"pid":"ef020549c16c6b84c59d2491292e60334b897388","tid":369530,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個post#390<br />\n想問下你話我人緣同愛情方面，結果竟然係摺埋一二邊仲開心，但我上年已經係咁樣喎，但依然好唔開心，咁摺埋一二邊，覺得自己一個開心啲其實係一種解決既方法定係點呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打</blockquote><br />\nbtw呢排活動識左個女仔，其實有冇發展機會呢，唔該"},{"pid":"4fc8a67c8b7e8516bbc923338fb774bcea44403a","tid":369530,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T21:28:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#479</span></span><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你的名字: kate<br />\n問題:今年內有機會再拍拖嗎？對一個男仔好似有小小意思但我唔係太分大家係乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n介唔介意比我問多題<br />\n想知下年仲有無機會讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n唔記得thanks bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n今年內有機會再拍拖嗎？<br />\n似有 關係仲睇落幾好<br />\n<br />\n對一個男仔好似有小小意思但我唔係太分大家係乜關係?<br />\n別想太多 人地對你冇乜意思<br />\n純粹當你係朋友<br />\n仲有佢好似覺得你份人好自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得係<br />\n<br />\n想知下年仲有無機會讀書?<br />\n我覺得有<br />\n你而家好似準備下定決心?</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴絲打 辛苦晒你地了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n承你貴言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  今年asso year two  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返一個sem追<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成績唔係差唔係好個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望下年可以入返u讀返自己中意個科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n最怕無書讀要出嚟做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於朋友個邊 其實自問自己對佢既感覺一時時  我自己都唔太清楚<br />\n感覺有時好似好朋友又好似好兄弟<br />\n好似傾得好開心 不過又無左種拍拖既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢覺得我自私我諗係有啲原因 成件事都好複雜下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都做過啲對唔住佢既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢咁諗係唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事實上我都係一個自私既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過除左呢個朋友 暫時都無乜對象可言  希望遇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問我未來既拍拖對象會唔會係我依家認識到/圈子入面既人？<br />\n事關我都唔知算唔算叫都有個人追我 但我對佢無興趣 甚至覺得佢好煩厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔知點拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9236bf0a36a22d446a934041f5d721d780986e42","tid":369530,"uid":78833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T23:18:05.000Z","msg":"上個POST #694<br />\n你的名字: 希<br />\n問題: 想問將來事業同前景? 而家讀緊大學, 就黎畢業<br />\n感情狀況？冇拍過拖, 個女仔會係D咩人?"},{"pid":"4d050ef3456c6a42eaeaa694140c5d6c2a906539","tid":369530,"uid":81262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T01:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>名：健<br />\n問題：暗戀女仔對我有冇好感？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">396</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖說係暗戀<br />\n但你對佢都好似幾主動熱情 係咪通常都係你聊佢<br />\n但唔見得有好感 未來你會變做好人 咩都就晒佢但冇回報</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打，我對佢一啲都唔主動熱情🤔 反而佢間中會聊我。會唔會占錯第2個女仔"},{"pid":"6bcf03ffc6033f596e56eb9d332c47d5e605b5d4","tid":369530,"uid":135196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"#893<br />\n你的名字: Alex<br />\n問題: 同鐘意既人仲有冇機？ 追左都好耐，但開始放棄"},{"pid":"7755e08559f04a5b9b37fda88b09874881898f46","tid":369530,"uid":17134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adf74feddc0ceb6bcb82cd4