post#390<br />\n想問下你話我人緣同愛情方面，結果竟然係摺埋一二邊仲開心，但我上年已經係咁樣喎，但依然好唔開心，咁摺埋一二邊，覺得自己一個開心啲其實係一種解決既方法定係點呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打</blockquote><br />\n我覺得你係睇開左<br />\n雖然好孤獨<br />\n但係你係當中搵到一啲自有自己一個人既時候既快樂咁可能<br />\n有時摺 都幾開心"},{"pid":"9f498ec29f3859600a22a7900f6e9afec8ea5aa3","tid":369530,"uid":70910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上個post#390<br />\n想問下你話我人緣同愛情方面，結果竟然係摺埋一二邊仲開心，但我上年已經係咁樣喎，但依然好唔開心，咁摺埋一二邊，覺得自己一個開心啲其實係一種解決既方法定係點呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打</blockquote><br />\nbtw呢排活動識左個女仔，其實有冇發展機會呢，唔該</blockquote><br />\n唔多似有<br />\n個女仔都好似幾活躍下 同埋幾中意享受生活咁<br />\n但始終你偏冷淡<br />\n佢好似冇乜為意你"},{"pid":"d355a7ba48ccc490061db545f5a99f29548a23d5","tid":369530,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T17:01:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇po link</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你終於開牌喇?</blockquote><br />\n打完機未眼瞓就開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b723ba4eefc65d700c46c67b9ca51617df3b19a","tid":369530,"uid":73039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇po link</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你終於開牌喇?</blockquote><br />\n打完機未眼瞓就開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未ocamp 咩？"},{"pid":"61be1d87ae075b8810068e80309a55cd9fa8804e","tid":369530,"uid":70910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:55:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#511</span></span><br />\n<blockquote>名字：yi <br />\n問題：返工識咗個同事，平時都有講兩句但唔多，想知佢點睇我同埋有無機會同佢發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該晒大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然你對佢有好感 而且都表現得幾熱情下<br />\n但係其實佢冇乜意慾同人發展<br />\n佢而家呢刻覺得自己一個比較自在<br />\n同埋本身都可能有啲煩惱困擾佢 <br />\n對愛情應該唔太熱衷咁<br />\n機會我唔覺得有啦<br />\n如果你太chur既話 仲有機會影響到大家本身關係<br />\n兩敗俱傷"},{"pid":"0b9250108cbed37fa2074e3e51d786a33e2fd58d","tid":369530,"uid":70910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#512</span></span></span><br />\n<blockquote>名字：jav w<br />\n問題：想問果個男仔鍾唔鍾意我 今年有無機會拍拖<br />\n唔該大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果個男仔對你冇好感 你太chur喇 因為個男仔本身好收埋自己情感唔俾人知 你就更關心太多 佔有慾太勁<br />\n反而嚇到對方<br />\n應該係<br />\n<br />\n今年冇拖拍 會越黎越恨拍拖 但亦都因為咁而闖禍 唔排除"},{"pid":"fc0808dd4db2b6d576c36277d64ff980df6c4397","tid":369530,"uid":70910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:10:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#516</span></span><br />\n<blockquote>你的名字: hazel<br />\n問題:<br />\n想問下同男朋友既發展會係點？<br />\n<br />\n唔該大師！：）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得黎緊發展都幾好 算唔錯 只係有少少失落<br />\n基本上你地兩個都會好好溝通<br />\n係而家好似有少少問題咁<br />\n男方有少少分手既意慾<br />\n未知係唔係因為你某啲決定<br />\n不過睇得出你好想同佢白頭到老咁"},{"pid":"7aac12203867d31b8b4db3a10aa55121db6d08b1","tid":369530,"uid":113371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">510</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99a008f69d593d5f1585296370731ab7405cccf","tid":369530,"uid":108152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf143be07a9c38760f2fa08e4b71efce888c1fed","tid":369530,"uid":125780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"677留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe70f3d60d6e6fd084483617852f313a1130833","tid":369530,"uid":3901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"913 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc3d9a8e0fc5dfb45fe2dcfadcc917b6ab247f1","tid":369530,"uid":98715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"上個post嘅人留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc0a05ee46acf4ddf865eb3c8b36579c901917e","tid":369530,"uid":11646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:19:57.000Z","msg":"888輕輕一推~"},{"pid":"c1c59425c54674031c7b0fae3b3b97086fcc2e1e","tid":369530,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>名稱：邦<br />\n問題：想問下目前遇到嘅對象有冇機會發展？佢都幾多人追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都想問下準備返新工 發展順唔順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">517</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n女方的確好多人追，因為佢對個個都唔差，同時佢都有其他選擇。依家你地關係唔差，但女仔似係睇緊你係咪合適，而你又好努力去追求佢。未來唔見有機會，你會有d野想去做去實行，但同一時間諗太多令自己最終無做到<br />\n<br />\n新工順利。係咪未接觸過既野？同同事會幾開心。"},{"pid":"b957f3b65dd2f913733992743ff45133acb8d13a","tid":369530,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>534</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d8d582262a1ce6387f23b378963c1f11766faf","tid":369530,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">552</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4aad9461bc12053712d0773fe5a4524b69a39f0","tid":369530,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>名：樂<br />\n問題：追緊身邊的女同事，一個月前都好有交流，但中間開始可能搵得太密，封左我Twitter，雖然約到出來玩，但唔似有下一次，我係咪應該放棄了？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>554</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n放棄啦<br />\n唔放棄既話你只係默默繼續付出到頭來睇住同第個人一齊。完。"},{"pid":"2f3cb4fca7602099a7939634af0d753270e647b5","tid":369530,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我的名字，晴晴<br />\n幾時先會出現真愛 一個肯為我付出同穩定既男人</blockquote><br />\n睇規則</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsorry巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我應該咁問，其實我有男朋友，但我哋中間已經出現少少問題，可唔可以問到佢係咪鍾意我？或者我應該點做好啲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>559</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n查實呢，睇牌呢，關係依家甚至未來唔覺有咩大問題。（但想問下你係咪有其他追求者？）但就咁睇應該男方新識左堆人而忽略左你？導致你覺得你付出多過佢，令你有d懷緬以前佢對你既好。建議你識多d人，同fd social下，因為依家你好似成個世界得你男友圍住佢轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1f4bfe36d366dec098841aa9b53635078505e8","tid":369530,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你的名字: min<br />\n問題:同心儀對象未來關係發展會點，如果唔多理想既話可以點樣去改善？<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>561</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n關係唔錯。但對方暫時似想維持依家關係。未來唔見會一齊，但應該會close左同幾enjoy個時既關係唔想有變。"},{"pid":"13e54e34d6d18452f3ddc877c7f4997de3cc6130","tid":369530,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你的名字:藍<br />\n問題:想問同男友關係未來發展,有咩要留意下? 同埋如果占卜結果係唔好嘅話可以做啲咩去改善? 唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>562</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n岩先拍無耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關係平平穩穩。但似男主動多過你。依家你成日ff太多幻想得太美好，建議你少ff多做事，自己主動返多dd. 唔好淨睇淨諗唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0523dceb93a7ebc3f04cedf770bac0978ccbff14","tid":369530,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>名字：Ying<br />\n問題：如無意外，9月master開學, 但因為之前出左d 問題，仲未confirm 實，成個過程都好似好有阻礙咁，想問未來一年讀書會順利？畢業後會搵到合適工作？ thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>569</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n順利。畢業後搵唔搵到好難講。因為你黎緊仲係讀書，咩工都未搵又未sd cv. 所以我read唔到。睇牌似係你畢業後要離開校園唔開心。你黎緊一年校園生活應該幾開心下。"},{"pid":"3def181def8be78d30a45b9ab4a741edf1809f12","tid":369530,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:25:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>名字：泳<br />\n問題：應該係外國繼續讀書好定返香港，同宜家男朋友係咪長久<br />\n<br />\n唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>571</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n留係外國讀書你都係想返香港，但繼續留就會幾開心下，但小心你感情事。<br />\n返左香港你生活會有變化，會開心既，但同時可能環境既轉變令你有少少不安。<br />\n<br />\n依家同男友關係好好，但未來關係可能會變差。但未到分手，可以話熱戀期過左平淡返落黎。但少不免會亂諗野。"}]}